Class NativeAdAdapter

  • java.lang.Object
    • android.widget.BaseAdapter
      • com.adiant.android.ads.NativeAdAdapter
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Adapter, ListAdapter, SpinnerAdapter

    public class NativeAdAdapter
extends BaseAdapter
    Adapter that wraps around another adapter in order to intersperse native ads among the adapter's items.
